description: This Chainlink VRF top 2% rating Chukcha purrs with a rating of 83, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 166, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 8 for North, 8 for East, Leverage for South, and Leverage for West. Chukcha has the personality suit of quant. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/30832-88661-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Chukcha [166 Votes, Top 2% Rating]
